values: "Hi. This is Anthony Crowley. Uh. I'm probably not in right now, or asleep, and busy, or something, but leave a message after the tone and I'll get right back to you. Ciao." arts by the divine (or possibly occult)

I've invited that brat, Draco Malfoy <lj user=barking_draco>, to my flat this afternoon to discuss a demonic career.  He's a wizard, so he can handle most of the miracling side of things.  And as far as I can tell he's good at making trouble.  I figure I'll take the little blighter on as an intern and he can do all the work and give me some time off.  Gives him decent prospects in the dark lord department too, so it's win-win.  <s>As if...</s>

<font size=-1><i>Note to self: Before bastard kid arrives, remove painting of Gabriel from bedroom.</font>
